31
00:01:34,799 --> 00:01:35,640
The letter says

32
00:01:36,719 --> 00:01:38,200
Crown Prince is colluding with Miao.

33
00:01:38,799 --> 00:01:40,040
Once he ascends to power,

34
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:42,680
he will form alliance with Miao,
and wage wars on others.

35
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:45,159
Then, I will expose you as an enemy spy,

36
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,359
in the court.

37
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:49,560
That would give me ample reason
to attack Sheng.

38
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:53,040
Your Highness, what should we do?

39
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:55,000
Send a message to rescue Chuyao back.

40
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:57,959
We should go to see Empress Dowager now.

41
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,560
Chu Yifan.

42
00:02:02,799 --> 00:02:04,239
How despicable and shameless.

43
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:08,319
I miss your sugar pills.

44
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:11,199
Isn't this the letter Chuyao sent to me?

45
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:13,280
How did it end up in your hands?

46
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,360
Sheng Yueling.

47
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:18,680
You are still of use to me now.

48
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:20,800
I've already rescued Chuyao.

49
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,719
Lord Wu is also willing to back me.

50
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,360
Now that my former men have reunited.

51
00:02:27,879 --> 00:02:29,280
It's time for you to step back.

52
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,560
If you name Chu Ruheng

53
