82
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:17,079
Are you trying to make me just go

83
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,680
from nothing to nothing?

84
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:20,680
Let me tell you.

85
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:23,079
If I cannot ascend to the throne today,

86
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,639
