87
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,600
Yue.

88
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,319
Don't move.

89
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,680
Or I'll kill her.

90
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:31,800
