98
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:51,439
It's because Concubine Yu won all love,

99
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:54,120
leaving not a shred to my mother.

100
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:56,360
The two of us
suffered enough humiliation.

101
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,560
In the end, my mother
died of depression.

102
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:03,279
I poisoned both Concubine Yu
and Lord Hui.

103
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,680
Forgot to tell you.

104
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:08,360
The attack on the Princess of Sheng

105
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:10,959
was also orchestrated by me.

106
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:12,959
As long as she dies,

107
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:15,680
I will have the reason to propose a war,

108
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,279
and accelerate my alliance with Miao.

109
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,879
You're the one who killed Princess.

110
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:23,240
I'll kill you.

111
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,560
Don't move.

112
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,360
Yue.

113
